flowchart LR
    subgraph CI["CI workflow (every push / PR)"]
        Dev([Developer]) --> PR[GitHub PR]
        PR --> Test[Lint + pytest]
        Test --> Build[docker build]
        Build --> Scan{Trivy CVE Scan}
        Scan -->|CRITICAL or HIGH| Fail([Fail])
        Scan -->|clean| Sign[Cosign keyless sign]
        Sign --> Push[Push to ECR]
    end

    subgraph CD["CD workflow (push to main only)"]
        Deploy[kubectl apply / Helm]
        Deploy --> Admit{Kyverno verifyImages}
        Admit -->|signature missing| Reject([Reject])
        Admit -->|signature valid| Run([Pod Running])
    end

    Push -.->|merge to main| Deploy

    classDef plain fill:#ffffff,stroke:#333,color:#000
    class Dev,PR,Test,Build,Scan,Sign,Push,Deploy,Admit,Run,Fail,Reject plain
